    dc:description "FIGURES 9–12. Sketches made by Meigen for plates used in Wiedemann’s works. 9, sketches for a study of wing venation and terminology. 10, sketches of Longina (top) and Laphria (bottom). 11, sketches of various Syrphidae. 12, sketches of Panops baudini. Sketches in senior author’s personal collection." ;
